# Adventure Game Brain Storm

## Theme

> - Maze theme
>
>   ### Objective 
>
>   - Get out of maze alive with any artifacts that you gather 
>   - MAIN artifact(s) is found in center of maze and the most difficult to get
>     - Must prove worthiness in order to pick up main artifact before we leave.
>       - we are thinking ( MjÃ¶lnir -  muh-yol-nir ) 

## Level Design

> - Trap doors that will drop you a level
>
> - Main stairway / path that would lead to center 
>
>   ### Dimensions
>
>   - 1m^2 

## Enemies / Obstacles

> - random "monsters" that we can turn on and off so we can debug successfully 
